title: RVCA Sideways Tour
description: The RVCA Sideways tour takes the crew skating through Belgium, while visiting a few breweries and abby's for some fine beer tasting. Sidewayers include: Julian Davidson, Jeremy Leabres, Charles Collet, Remy Taviera, Octavio Barrera and Yann-Xavier Horowitz. Video by Lucas Fiederling. Song Derek's Blues by Natural Child.
